tle a:font-normal\">L</span><span class=\"a:m-0 a:font-functional a:text-sm a:text-content-subtle a:font-normal\">XL</span></div></div></div></div></div></a><div class=\"as-t-box as-t-box--relative as-m-product-tile__area as-m-product-tile__area-tertiary\"></div></div></div><div data-testid=\"lister-empty-result-container\"></div></div><div class=\"a:order-3 a:lg:order-1\"><div class=\"a:pt-2\"><div class=\"a:flex a:justify-center\"></div></div></div><div class=\"a:order-3 a:lg:order-1\"><div class=\"a:py-4 a:lg:py-6\"><div>\n\t\n\t\t<div class=\"text__container  \">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"a:prose a:font-functional a:font-normal a:text-base a:text-content-neutral \">\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p><b>READ: <a href=\"https://www.snowandrock.com/expert-advice-and-inspiration/buying-guides/the-mid-layer-buying-guide.html?from=lister\">MID LAYER BUYING GUIDE</a> / <a href=\"https://www.snowandrock.com/expert-advice-and-inspiration/buying-guides/dont-forget-your-thermals.html?from=lister\">DON'T FORGET YOUR THERMALS</a></b></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"read-more\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" class=\"read-more__state\" id=\"expand-text-id-1193317166\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tSnow+Rock is the place to find the best <b>women's fleeces </b>and <b>mid-layers</b>. We stock an extensive\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"read-more__target\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\thand-picked selection of stylish performance mid-layers and fleeces to suit any adventure. All from top brands including <b><a href=\"https://www.snowandrock.com/brands/passenger.html\">Passenger</a>, <a href=\"https://www.snowandrock.com/brands/patagonia.html\">Patagonia,</a> </b>and <a href=\"https://www.snowandrock.com/brands/the-north-face.html\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">The North Face</a>. Our fleeces and mid-layers are ideal for staying<b> warm and comfortable </b>in cold weather. They're ideal for winter sports such as skiing and snowboarding as well as everyday wear. Using <b>versatile designs </b>and fabrics, they can also be used for added insulation on colder nights. If you're looking for the best women's fleeces and mid-layers, look no further. We have a wide selection of products from top brands, to keep you prepared, insulated, and comfortable for the upcoming seasons with our <a href=\"https://www.snowandrock.com/c/ski/clothing/fleeces-midlayers.html\">ski fleeces</a>, <a href=\"https://www.snowandrock.com/c/snowboard/clothing/fleece-midlayers.html\">snowboard fleeces,</a> and <a href=\"https://www.snowandrock.com/c/new/clothing.html\">new-season clothing.</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<label for=\"expand-text-id-1193317166\" class=\"read-more__trigger\"> Read less </label>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<label for=\"expand-text-id-1193317166\" class=\"read-more__trigger\">Read more</label>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\n\n</div></div></div></div></div></div>\n \n\t \n\t \n\t\t \n\t\t \n\t\t \n\t\n        \n    \n\t\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n\t\n\t<div class=\"responsive-columns parbase\">\n\n\n<div class=\"a:grid a:grid-cols-12  a:grid-content a:gap-x-2 a:md:gap-x-4 a:xl:gap-x-6\">\n\t\n\t<div class=\" a:col-span-12 a:sm:col-span-3\">\n\n\n<div class=\"aem-Grid aem-Grid--12 aem-Grid--default--12 \">\n    \n    \n    \n</div>\n</div>\n\n\t\n\t<div class=\" a:col-span-12 a:sm:col-span-8\">\n\n\n<div class=\"aem-Grid aem-Grid--12 aem-Grid--default--12 \">\n    \n    <div class=\"collapsible-list base-component-ssr parbase aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--12\">\n\n\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t \n\t \n\t\t<div data-hypernova-key=\"AEMScenes_CollapsibleList\" data-hypernova-id=\"e51e6d5b-52c1-4614-9627-a7cdce683311\"><div class=\"as-m-collapse as-m-collapse--animation-height\"><input type=\"checkbox\" class=\"as-m-collapse__toggle\" id=\"collapsible-list-item-9c2181bdfd\" value=\"collapsible-list-item-9c2181bdfd\"><div class=\"as-m-collapse__header as-m-collapse__header--with-hover\"><label class=\"as-a-label as-m-collapse__header-label as-m-collapse__header-label--gutter-medium as-m-collapse__header-label--with-icon\" for=\"collapsible-list-item-9c2181bdfd\"><span class=\"as-a-label__content\"><span role=\"img\" class=\"as-a-icon as-a-icon--chevron-down as-a-icon--action as-a-icon--minor as-m-collapse__icon as-m-collapse__icon-vertical--center as-m-collapse__icon-horizontal--right\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" focusable=\"false\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"as-a-icon__svg\"><path d=\"M12 17.667 2 8.215 4.344 6 12 13.236 19.656 6 22 8.215l-10 9.452Z\"></path></svg></span><div class=\"as-a-text\"><strong>What are the main benefits of women’s fleeces for outdoor activities?</strong></div></span></label></div><div class=\"as-m-collapse__body\"><div class=\"a:py-4\"><div class=\"a:m-0 a:font-functional a:text-base a:font-normal\"><div><p>Women’s fleeces offer excellent warmth and insulation by trapping heat close to the body, making them ideal for cold weather. They’re lightweight, breathable, and quick-drying, allowing moisture to escape and keeping you comfortable during active pursuits like hiking, skiing, or walking.&nbsp;</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"as-a-divider as-a-divider--horizontal as-m-collapse__divider\" role=\"separator\"></div></div><div class=\"as-m-collapse as-m-collapse--animation-height\"><input type=\"checkbox\" class=\"as-m-collapse__toggle\" id=\"collapsible-list-item-fa522bc7a2\" value=\"collapsible-list-item-fa522bc7a2\"><div class=\"as-m-collapse__header as-m-collapse__header--with-hover\"><label class=\"as-a-label as-m-collapse__header-label as-m-collapse__header-label--gutter-medium as-m-collapse__header-label--with-icon\" for=\"collapsible-list-item-fa522bc7a2\"><span class=\"as-a-label__content\"><span role=\"img\" class=\"as-a-icon as-a-icon--chevron-down as-a-icon--action as-a-icon--minor as-m-collapse__icon as-m-collapse__icon-vertical--center as-m-collapse__icon-horizontal--right\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" focusable=\"false\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"as-a-icon__svg\"><path d=\"M12 17.667 2 8.215 4.344 6 12 13.236 19.656 6 22 8.215l-10 9.452Z\"></path></svg></span><div class=\"as-a-text\"><strong>Are women’s fleeces suitable for layering?</strong></div></span></label></div><div class=\"as-m-collapse__body\"><div class=\"a:py-4\"><div class=\"a:m-0 a:font-functional a:text-base a:font-normal\"><div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yes, fleeces are perfect for layering. Their lightweight and versatile design means they can be worn comfortably over base layers or under waterproof jackets, adapting easily to changing weather conditions without adding bulk.&nbsp;</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"as-a-divider as-a-divider--horizontal as-m-collapse__divider\" role=\"separator\"></div></div><div class=\"as-m-collapse as-m-collapse--animation-height\"><input type=\"checkbox\" class=\"as-m-collapse__toggle\" id=\"collapsible-list-item-fbfcc57d3b\" value=\"collapsible-list-item-fbfcc57d3b\"><div class=\"as-m-collapse__header as-m-collapse__header--with-hover\"><label class=\"as-a-label as-m-collapse__header-label as-m-collapse__header-label--gutter-medium as-m-collapse__header-label--with-icon\" for=\"collapsible-list-item-fbfcc57d3b\"><span class=\"as-a-label__content\"><span role=\"img\" class=\"as-a-icon as-a-icon--chevron-down as-a-icon--action as-a-icon--minor as-m-collapse__icon as-m-collapse__icon-vertical--center as-m-collapse__icon-horizontal--right\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" focusable=\"false\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"as-a-icon__svg\"><path d=\"M12 17.667 2 8.215 4.344 6 12 13.236 19.656 6 22 8.215l-10 9.452Z\"></path></svg></span><div class=\"as-a-text\"><strong>How do fleeces compare to other types of jackets in terms of comfort and weight?</strong></div></span></label></div><div class=\"as-m-collapse__body\"><div class=\"a:py-4\"><div class=\"a:m-0 a:font-functional a:text-base a:font-normal\"><div><p>Fleeces are softer and lighter than many insulated or down jackets. The fabric’s plush texture feels comfortable against the skin, and the material’s low weight makes fleeces easy to pack and wear for extended periods without feeling heavy or stuffy.&nbsp;</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"as-a-divider as-a-divider--horizontal as-m-collapse__divider\" role=\"separator\"></div></div><div class=\"as-m-collapse as-m-collapse--animation-height\"><input type=\"checkbox\" class=\"as-m-collapse__toggle\" id=\"collapsible-list-item-b3f5746f53\" value=\"collapsible-list-item-b3f5746f53\"><div class=\"as-m-collapse__header as-m-collapse__header--with-hover\"><label class=\"as-a-label as-m-collapse__header-label as-m-collapse__header-label--gutter-medium as-m-collapse__header-label--with-icon\" for=\"collapsible-list-item-b3f5746f53\"><span class=\"as-a-label__content\"><span role=\"img\" class=\"as-a-icon as-a-icon--chevron-down as-a-icon--action as-a-icon--minor as-m-collapse__icon as-m-collapse__icon-vertical--center as-m-collapse__icon-horizontal--right\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" focusable=\"false\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"as-a-icon__svg\"><path d=\"M12 17.667 2 8.215 4.344 6 12 13.236 19.656 6 22 8.215l-10 9.452Z\"></path></svg></span><div class=\"as-a-text\"><strong>Are fleeces water-resistant or waterproof?</strong></div></span></label></div><div class=\"as-m-collapse__body\"><div class=\"a:py-4\"><div class=\"a:m-0 a:font-functional a:text-base a:font-normal\"><div><p>Fleeces are generally water-resistant, meaning they can handle light drizzles or snow but are not fully waterproof. For heavy rain, it’s best to pair a fleece with a waterproof shell. Their quick-drying nature ensures they remain comfortable even if they get damp.&nbsp;</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"as-a-divider as-a-divider--horizontal as-m-collapse__divider\" role=\"separator\"></div></div><div class=\"as-m-collapse as-m-collapse--animation-height\"><input type=\"checkbox\" class=\"as-m-collapse__toggle\" id=\"collapsible-list-item-0e90c24895\" value=\"collapsible-list-item-0e90c24895\"><div class=\"as-m-collapse__header as-m-collapse__header--with-hover\"><label class=\"as-a-label as-m-collapse__header-label as-m-collapse__header-label--gutter-medium as-m-collapse__header-label--with-icon\" for=\"collapsible-list-item-0e90c24895\"><span class=\"as-a-label__content\"><span role=\"img\" class=\"as-a-icon as-a-icon--chevron-down as-a-icon--action as-a-icon--minor as-m-collapse__icon as-m-collapse__icon-vertical--center as-m-collapse__icon-horizontal--right\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" focusable=\"false\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"as-a-icon__svg\"><path d=\"M12 17.667 2 8.215 4.344 6 12 13.236 19.656 6 22 8.215l-10 9.452Z\"></path></svg></span><div class=\"as-a-text\"><strong>What features should I look for in a women’s fleece jacket?</strong></div></span></label></div><div class=\"as-m-collapse__body\"><div class=\"a:py-4\"><div class=\"a:m-0 a:font-functional a:text-base a:font-normal\"><div><p>Look for features like full-length zippers for ventilation, zippered pockets for secure storage, adjustable hems, and fitted hoods for extra warmth. Some fleeces also offer reinforced areas for durability and are available in various thicknesses to suit different activities and temperatures.&nbsp;</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"as-a-divider as-a-divider--horizontal as-m-collapse__divider\" role=\"separator\"></div></div></div>\n \n\t \n\t \n\t\t \n\t\t \n\t\t \n\t\n\t\n\n\n\n</div>\n\n    \n</div>\n</div>\n\n\t\n\t<div class=\" a:col-span-12 a:sm:col-span-1 a:md:col-span-2 a:lg:col-span-1\">\n\n\n<div class=\"aem-Grid aem-Grid--12 aem-Grid--default--12 \">\n    \n    \n    \n</div